{"tid":1409400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片] 警畜：我屌你老母呀","createTime":"2019-08-04T20:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T21:20:37.000Z","uid":266968,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6559b9ebdd17038596b5b4d205e972f4adb1de44","tid":1409400,"uid":266968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:59:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkon9agroup/permalink/2999271436780567/?sfnsn=mo&amp;s=100010795742309&amp;w=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkon9agroup%2Fpermalink%2F2999271436780567%2F%3Fsfnsn%3Dmo%26s%3D100010795742309%26w%3Dn&d=nzz81mtU0v8QN53TvL9QoYICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=bfc14f81\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkon9agroup/permalink/2999271436780567/?sfnsn=mo&amp;s=100010795742309&amp;w=n</a>"},{"pid":"7bd4b97ba4b9c1a15de04fa0fcdb9c1d96c56602","tid":1409400,"uid":266968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:00:09.000Z","msg":"趕時間00:19開始"},{"pid":"825a01c8f8113cf3f22047e44e07ae08fa85562a","tid":1409400,"uid":150742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:00:44.000Z","msg":"[請廣傳] FORWARDED FROM TELEGRAM<br />\n朋友既朋友 警隊臨床心理學家指出唔少警察<br />\n長期聽到針對警察示威口號產生幻聽、躁鬱、最嚴重會患上抑鬱等<br />\n<br />\n若示威者同警察距離非常近既時候, 利用群眾優勢<br />\n不要說「黑警，可恥」, 試著說「黑社會」,這種標籤化令警察內心會感自愧, 壓力倍僧, 行為自動檢點<br />\n<br />\n進一步造成心理創傷口號，不要說「香港警察，知法犯法」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">試著說「不畏懼、不徇私、不對他人懷惡意」</span>此口號出自警察誓言, 當有人不斷叫出此口號，警察會回憶畢業既誓言，開始對自己身份認同產生懷疑同混淆, 精神疲乏, 有部份警察雙眼通紅、帶有淚光<br />\n<br />\n終極核彈級口號, 有機會造成永久心理創傷, 相信好快用得「殺人兇手」 當事實真的發生，不論兇手有沒有殺人，身處同一個群體，都變成兇手, 不單面對極大壓力而崩塌, 伴隨的是恐懼、抑鬱, 更重要是這種負面情緒會災難性地爆發傳遍整個群體"},{"pid":"f18bccb4758ee4a2d6039a00d08bc051733e9d6c","tid":1409400,"uid":266968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:10:38.000Z","msg":"仲有條係街坊係屋企影落黎，黑警竟然舉棍大叫落黎呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"81a167d4bee6bdba72420d158dad7be4cdfd3745","tid":1409400,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:11:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3d02e90b9fc36ca5fbb85e6d1facbde799a61a8","tid":1409400,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:20:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}